Photo by 50 Cent on August 21, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Hundreds of fans of Curtis "50 Cent" Jackson line up on the sidewalk outside Hy-Vee and the former Gordmans store Friday in North Peoria. The popular rapper was in town to promote his line of liquors, Branson Cognac and Le Chemin du Roi Champagne and to sign autographs. MATT DAYHOFF/JOURNAL STAR JJ BULLOCK txt JOURNAL STAR 18 hours ago f Over ,000 people waited in a line that snaked from the front door into the parking lot at Peoria's Grand Prairie Hy-Vee on Friday in sweltering heat, and not because the store was giving away free groceries.'.
